Name: Ino
About the game: INO is a short Adventure/Horror story driven game. It tells the story of Kaede and Hitaki, two classmates that get involved with a mysterious girl called Ino. Follow the story as they try to figure out who she is while they try to escape from being murdered. Features: - Unique maps with original graphic assets - Chase system to keep you on your toes - Puzzles to test your wits - Character driven story
